

## üìö Tabel: `users`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data    | Keterangan                    |
| ----------- | ------------ | ----------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK)  | ID unik pengguna              |
| name        | VARCHAR(100) | Nama lengkap                  |
| email       | VARCHAR(100) | Email unik                    |
| password    | STRING       | Hash password                 |
| role        | ENUM         | `student`, `teacher`, `admin` |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP    |                               |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP    |                               |

---

## üéì Tabel: `classes`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data    | Keterangan                  |
| ----------- | ------------ | --------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK)  | ID unik kelas               |
| name        | VARCHAR(100) | Nama kelas                  |
| teacher\_id | BIGINT (FK)  | Relasi ke `users.id` (guru) |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP    |                             |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP    |                             |

---

## üßë‚Äçüè´ Tabel: `class_students`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data   | Keterangan                   |
| ----------- | ----------- | ---------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK) |                              |
| class\_id   | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `classes.id`       |
| student\_id | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `users.id` (siswa) |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                              |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                              |

---

## üìù Tabel: `tasks`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data   | Keterangan                      |
| ----------- | ----------- | ------------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK) | ID unik tugas                   |
| student\_id | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `users.id`            |
| date        | DATE        | Tanggal tugas                   |
| punishment  | BOOLEAN     | Apakah tugas ini karena hukuman |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                                 |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                                 |

---

## üß† Tabel: `task_words`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data   | Keterangan           |
| ----------- | ----------- | -------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK) |                      |
| task\_id    | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `tasks.id` |
| word        | VARCHAR(50) | Kosakata             |
| description | TEXT        | Deskripsi kosakata   |
| example     | TEXT        | Contoh kalimat       |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                      |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                      |

---

## üåü Tabel: `task_scores`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data   | Keterangan                  |
| ----------- | ----------- | --------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK) |                             |
| task\_id    | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `tasks.id`        |
| teacher\_id | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `users.id` (guru) |
| star\_count | TINYINT     | 1, 2, atau 3 bintang        |
| comment     | TEXT        | Komentar guru               |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                             |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                             |

---

## üìÑ Tabel: `materials`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data       | Keterangan                        |
| ----------- | --------------- | --------------------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK)     | ID unik materi                    |
| title       | VARCHAR(100)    | Judul materi                      |
| content     | TEXT            | Konten materi                     |
| file\_url   | TEXT (nullable) | URL file (PDF/video) jika ada     |
| created\_by | BIGINT (FK)     | Relasi ke `users.id` (guru/admin) |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP       |                                   |
| updated\_at | TIMESTAMP       |                                   |

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Tabel: `activity_logs`

| Kolom       | Tipe Data   | Keterangan           |
| ----------- | ----------- | -------------------- |
| id          | BIGINT (PK) |                      |
| user\_id    | BIGINT (FK) | Relasi ke `users.id` |
| activity    | TEXT        | Deskripsi aktivitas  |
| created\_at | TIMESTAMP   |                      |

